      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Games That Fit the Scene" } }
      }
    },
    "飲み会・旅行・キャンプ・カップル・リモート飲み……\nどの場面でもアプリが3つ提案します。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Drinking parties, trips, camping, couples, remote hangouts...\nThe app suggests three games for any occasion." } }
      }
    },
    "道具はアプリで" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Tools Built In" } }
      }
    },
    "サイコロ・トランプ・コイン・ルーレット・タイマー・お題ガチャ・王様くじ。\n手ぶらでも遊べます。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Dice, cards, coin, roulette, timer, prompt gacha, king's game.\nYou can play empty-handed." } }
      }
    },
    "あなたの一票が育てる" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Grown by Your Votes" } }
      }
    },
    "👍👎で精度が上がり、アイデア箱で新しいゲームを追加。\n使うほど自分に合う提案に。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "👍👎 sharpen the suggestions; the idea box adds new games.\nIt fits you better the more you use it." } }
